WHO   — GURREN LAGANN — an entertainment sphere — an anime-world
WHAT  — A boy who digs holes underground finds a tiny face-shaped robot and a buried drill, and a hot-blooded stranger who tells him the sky is real. From a hole in the earth, Gurren Lagann spirals up and up — through a tyrant, through the moon, through galaxies — on pure willpower and ever-larger drills. The blueprint for everything Trigger would later build: escalation as a philosophy.
